name: Sequential Workflow
type: Handler
description: |
  Conversation handler.
  Executes a list of workflow steps in order when matching events arrive on the
  bound channel. As a Handler, it may emit events and request document patches.
steps:
  type: List
  itemType: Sequential Workflow Step
  description: Ordered list of steps to execute (positional semantics).
channel:
  type: Text
  description: Contracts-map key of the channel this handler binds to (same scope).
event:
  description: >
    Optional matcher payload used by the handlerâ€™s processor to further restrict
    which incoming events from `channel` are handled.
